00:04:44.992 --> 00:04:47.003
These are perfect for that 2 p.m. slump

00:04:47.003 --> 00:04:48.303
when you just feel a little peckish

00:04:48.303 --> 00:04:50.559
and you need something to
tide you over until dinner.

00:04:50.559 --> 00:04:52.408
First up I'm going to make these delicious

00:04:52.408 --> 00:04:54.277
little cottage cheese fruit cups.

00:04:54.277 --> 00:04:56.211
All I'm doing is putting about half a cup

00:04:56.211 --> 00:04:58.178
of cottage cheese at the
bottom of the mason jar.

00:04:58.178 --> 00:04:59.761
And then I've got some beautiful melon

00:04:59.761 --> 00:05:01.388
that I just finely chopped up.

00:05:01.388 --> 00:05:03.236
And I'm topping it with some red grapes.

00:05:03.236 --> 00:05:05.675
These are a great snack to
fill you up really quickly

00:05:05.675 --> 00:05:08.424
and again, get you through to dinner.

00:05:09.193 --> 00:05:11.546
Finally, I've got these
super simple deli roll-ups.

00:05:11.546 --> 00:05:12.826
All I do is take a piece of turkey

00:05:12.826 --> 00:05:15.097
and a piece of cheese and roll them up.

